               <p>The prisoner was <rs id="t17840915-150-deflabel697" type="occupation">servant</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840915-150-defend1314 t17840915-150-deflabel697"></join> in my warehouse; the skins were found upon the prisoner; he acknowledged taking the skins; no promises were made him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17840915-150-person1322">
                  JOHN
                   BAGLEY
